      "**Alternate** angles lie between the two lines on opposite sides of the transversal (a Z position).",
      "**Co-interior** angles lie between the two lines on the same side of the transversal (a C position).",
      "First decide which angles are **interior**: they lie in the strip between the two crossed lines."
